Answer.Comments: I was very interested in this survey before I started the task, but it was very difficult for me to memorize the correct words and gestures because the sequences were very confused.  Nonetheless, I enjoyed the task and I tried to complete this survey as accurately as I could with my best ability.  Hopefully, my poor performance could be useful for the researchers.  Thanks.

Answer.Comments: It would certainly be better if you provided a chance for a break! At first I did not understand the directions--as is reflected by my survey. Surely it is not necessary to have it be so long! Also curious you didn't ask age, considering the fact that most people have a poorer memory when they get older. (60 year old case in point here)
